Set default workbench settings for web mode

Configures the web workbench to start without a welcome page and with
the secondary sidebar hidden by default. Also supports ?theme= and ?label=
query parameters to set the color theme and command center label.
Disables extension signature verification (Code-OSS lacks Microsoft's signing infrastructure).

